gobblin.service.modules.scheduler

Class GobblinServiceJobScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
      • gobblin.scheduler.JobScheduler
        • gobblin.service.modules.scheduler.GobblinServiceJobScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service, SpecCatalogListener

    @Alpha
public class GobblinServiceJobScheduler
extends JobScheduler
implements SpecCatalogListener
    An extension to JobScheduler that is also a SpecCatalogListener. GobblinServiceJobScheduler listens for new / updated FlowSpec and schedules and runs them via Orchestrator.
